OL,3,CAnimal charity backs 'largest ever'
OL,4,Crescue of bears from illegal farm
OL,6,FA Sussex animal charity has thrown its
OL,7,Fbacking behind a major rescue
OL,8,Foperation involving 27 young bears in
OL,9,FLaos.
OL,11,FThe Uckfield-based International
OL,12,FAnimal Rescue has hailed the plan by
OL,13,FFree the Bears, which is believed to
OL,14,Fbe the largest ever rescue of the
OL,15,Fanimals in South East Asia.
OL,17,FIt saw 27 moon bears - also known as
OL,18,FAsiatic black bears - saved from an
OL,19,Fillegal bile farm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
