PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1780041898
OL,3,CAnimal charity backs 'largest ever'
OL,4,Crescue of bears from illegal farm
OL,6,FThe facility has since been shut down
OL,7,Fby Laos authorities, and the bears -
OL,8,Fwhich are all believed to be between
OL,9,Fone and three years old - resettled at
OL,10,Fthe organisation's wildlife sanctuary.
OL,12,FIts CEO, Matt Hunt, said the rescue is
OL,13,Fan "incredible milestone" which
OL,14,F"represents a long-term commitment to
OL,15,Fevery one of these bears".
OL,17,FHe added: "We're ready to give them
OL,18,Fsafe, healthy lives they deserve. But
OL,19,Fwe really can't do it alone."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
