OL,3,CAnimal charity backs 'largest ever'
OL,4,Crescue of bears from illegal farm
OL,6,FTo cope with the added financial
OL,7,Fburden of caring for its new arrivals,
OL,8,Fthe charity has set up a fundraising
OL,9,Fpage, with an overall target of
OL,10,F$300,000 (#223,000).
OL,12,FIt says it will use the money to build
OL,13,Fnew enclosures and hire more staff.
